<plot>Judy is a video about a woman's relationship with her abuser/husband.  It chronicles her relationship with him, the escalation of the abuse, and her escape.  This emotional, insightful, and disturbing video could be any woman's story and demonstrates that fiction and fact aren't always strangers. It illuminates the hidden reality of distractive dependency.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?280625</url></doc>
